data.description: Don't miss this IMMACULATE, MOVE-IN READY 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath home located in the Enclave of Imperial Lakes with a BRAND NEW ROOF in 10/23. NEW A/C SYSTEM  INSTALLED in 12/23!! The home sits on a 0.21 acre CORNER LOT with an IRRIGATION SYSTEM  and lots of room for a pool, gazebo or fire pit. The INTERIOR and EXTERIOR have been FRESHLY PAINTED in neutral tones, and BRAND NEW LUXURY VINYL PLANK FLOORING has been installed throughout!! The well-designed floor plan offers an excellent use of space in it's 1,466 SF. The kitchen has light color cabinetry with brushed nickel hardware, stainless steel appliances, double sinks with garbage disposal, closet pantry and a SEPARATE DINING AREA. The Great Room has a CEILING FAN and a sliding glass door opening up to a COVERED AND SCREENED PATIO. The generous-sized MASTER BEDROOM SUITE has a CEILING FAN, EN-SUITE BATH with a DOUBLE SINK VANITY, GARDEN TUB with SEPARATE SHOWER, PRIVATE WATER CLOSET, and 2 LARGE WALK-IN CLOSETS. This is a great VALUE with NEW ROOF, NEW A/C SYSTEM, NEW LUXURY VINYL PLANK FLOORS, AND FRESHLY PAINTED EXTERIOR AND INTERIOR!!
